{"tid":1414602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出面班手足幫你打生打死，屌你老母成班割乜撚呀","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:14:04.000Z","uid":19255,"like":72,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4185393a538a305af12f3e545e973342224b731a","tid":1414602,"uid":19255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:32:01.000Z","msg":"講就核彈都唔割，依家小小火就係度話好暴力呀，改觀啦，唔支持啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母班兄弟幫你打生打死，出錢出力，你講啲咁嘅嘢？係度摞道德光環？如果你係網軍製造分化，我唔怪你。但如果你係自己人，我真心覺得好撚失望。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你只不過係勝利球迷姐。<br />\n<br />\n無論你點講都好，其實根本我地就係一場革命，你叫口號果陣冇意識到咩？<br />\n<br />\n革命不是請客吃飯，不能那樣優雅呀！如果我地用愛與和平真係感化到敵人，邊個會選擇激進呀！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0179a49dc9e11b7e2f80c0a10f3ebc4d1f0e6f64","tid":1414602,"uid":19255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce4f0bed9c02742a81ffc882747ff6951fa78fd","tid":1414602,"uid":4496,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:32:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>出面黑色三毛警示生效<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日好多三毛扮和理非出分化post</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4e9c7520834a3f423b472cdf6f5cf5a3c85fd5ba","tid":1414602,"uid":19255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9ca399eceb7e235d2c3077c0558dbdaf4b5620","tid":1414602,"uid":19255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ce4f0bed9c02742a81ffc882747ff6951fa78fd","tid":1414602,"uid":4496,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:32:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>出面黑色三毛警示生效<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日好多三毛扮和理非出分化post</strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:33:18.000Z","